  "literalTranslation": {
    "wordAligned": "and thus We resurrected them [so] that they might question one another. Said a speaker from among them \"how long did you remain?\" They said \"we remained a day or part of a day.\" They said \"Your Lord is most knowing about what you remained. So send one of you with your silver coin this to the city and let him look [for] which is the best of food so let him bring to you with provision from it and let him be cautious and let not anyone make aware about you [anyone]."
  },
